SUMMARY:Andy: A Dog’s Tale
DESCRIPTION:Watch the award-winning short film\, Andy: A Dog’s Tale\, with the team who brought the movie to life\, including director Jamy Wheless\, Jean Schulz\, and Canine Companions dogs and trainers.
URL:https://schulzmuseum.org/event/a-dogs-tale/
