SUMMARY:Homeschool Day: Snoopy’s Family
DESCRIPTION:Explore the Museum’s newest exhibition\, Snoopy’s Family\, and learn about animal families\, build animal homes\, learn to draw Snoopy\, and more. Also\, ice skate at Snoopy’s Home Ice from 12:30–2:00 pm. Early registration encouraged\, as this event typically sells out.
URL:https://schulzmuseum.org/event/homeschool-day-snoopys-family/
CATEGORIES:Calendar of Events
END:VEVENT
