SUMMARY:Museum Mondays for Little Ones: Spring into Fun
DESCRIPTION:On the last Monday of the month\, enjoy stories\, crafts\, and activities designed for children ages 1-5 and their caregivers. This month\, add a spring to your step and celebrate the season with hands-on crafts. Paint a bird’s nest\, make a squish art butterfly\, and blow bubbles to create art.
URL:https://schulzmuseum.org/event/museum-mondays-for-little-ones-spring-into-fun/
CATEGORIES:Calendar of Events
