SUMMARY:Comic Artist Badge Workshop
DESCRIPTION:Girl Scout Cadettes are invited to earn their Comic Artist badge in this special hands-on workshop at the Schulz Museum. Museum staff will teach Cadettes how to develop stories and characters and create a four-panel comic strip from beginning to end while completing all five steps of the Comic Artist badge. Advanced registration required.
URL:https://schulzmuseum.org/event/comic-artist-badge-workshop-11/
CATEGORIES:Calendar of Events
END:VEVENT
