SUMMARY:Graphic Medicine: Mom’s Cancer with Brian Fies
DESCRIPTION:Join award-winning cartoonist Brian Fies to celebrate the 20th anniversary of his ground-breaking graphic memoir\, Mom’s Cancer\, which won the first-ever Eisner Award for Best Digital Comic.
URL:https://schulzmuseum.org/event/graphic-medicine-moms-cancer-with-brian-fies/
CATEGORIES:Calendar of Events
END:VEVENT
