SUMMARY:Entertainment Technology Badge Workshop
DESCRIPTION:Girl Scout Juniors are invited to earn their Entertainment Technology badge by completing all five steps at the Schulz Museum. Participants will have fun creating short movies using a green screen and sound effects while completing other hands-on technology challenges. Advanced registration required.
URL:https://schulzmuseum.org/event/entertainment-technology-badge-workshop-8/
