SUMMARY:Museum Mondays for Little Ones: Mudding Around
DESCRIPTION:On the last Monday of the month\, enjoy stories\, crafts\, and activities designed for children ages 1-5 and their caregivers. This month\, hop into summer with hands-on nature and garden crafts. Stamp a polka-dot snail\, blow a blooming bubble garden\, and fingerpaint a fantastic frog.
URL:https://schulzmuseum.org/event/museum-mondays-for-little-ones-mudding-around/
