SUMMARY:Summer Science (Grades 1-3)
DESCRIPTION:Explore the science of summer with sun-powered experiments. Build the ultimate bug catcher\, create chemical reactions\, bake solar s’mores\, blow rainbow bubbles\, and cool off with hands-on water play.
URL:https://schulzmuseum.org/event/summer-science-grades-1-3-7/
CATEGORIES:Classes & Camps
END:VEVENT
