SUMMARY:LEGO Animation 1 (Grades 1-3)
DESCRIPTION:Build sets and characters with LEGOs\, then create a short stop-motion movie using iPads. Work in groups to add special effects\, dialogue\, and music!
URL:https://schulzmuseum.org/event/lego-animation-1-grades-1-3-8/
