SUMMARY:You’re Making That Up 1 (Grades 1-3)
DESCRIPTION:Have fun learning improv acting with acting instructor Annie Cooper. In this fun\, safe\, supportive environment\, kids of all skill levels will enjoy playing new and classic improv games that build creativity\, encourage quick thinking\, foster empathy\, and help them be flexible\, collaborative team members. Let’s have fun and make stuff up together!
URL:https://schulzmuseum.org/event/youre-making-that-up-1-grades-1-3/
CATEGORIES:Classes & Camps
