SUMMARY:Acting for Peanuts 1 (Grades 1-3)
DESCRIPTION:Explore theater arts while bringing Peanuts to life on the Schulz Museum’s stage! Learn stage terminology\, dive into script reading and writing\, play improv games\, and wrap it up by acting in a mini performance based on Charles Schulz’s Peanuts comic strips. Instructor: Annie Cooper
